{"tid":152975,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"各位睇中醫既巴打注意","createTime":"2017-03-12T08:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T14:57:13.000Z","uid":9344,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c76e5cfba6acb238dd0a8dc75e11bfc07139799","tid":152975,"uid":9344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"唔好幫襯用農本坊藥粉既診所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要食就食煲出黎果D中藥，一係磨出黎既藥粉都好，<br />\n總之唔好係農本坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你試過食傳統中藥再去試食農本坊既中藥，<br />\n就會發覺農本坊既所謂「夥粒」沖出黎真係淡撚過屎，<br />\n飲完好似冇飲過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之食中藥就唔好懶，最好食返傳統既煲藥;<br />\n就算係坊間一般賣緊既中藥粉都好，<br />\n都唔好試農本坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16880e6d535895f34f72ed4ebb79d43715924dce","tid":152975,"uid":1494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咩事睇中醫其實"},{"pid":"0ff4d9df2683b5fe3b3709520cc51b6e237fa156","tid":152975,"uid":9344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:49:08.000Z","msg":"氣虛頭暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋個人好重火氣<br />\nBtw咁都俾你搵到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c570e7ee4941134cf2e2b60397f0c69f252dfe95","tid":152975,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:05:56.000Z","msg":"但係幾多G佢都列明存喎<br />\n<br />\n你意思係佢QC做假?"},{"pid":"b26bb46800ab3ac49d609eef496d5e2be3bfbd9e","tid":152975,"uid":9344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:08:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係幾多G佢都列明存喎<br />\n<br />\n你意思係佢QC做假?</blockquote><br />\n有機會係不斷提取同壓縮既過程裏面令到中藥既營養流走左<br />\n我唔識形容，總之沖出黎好淡好淡，同飲開既中藥好唔同"},{"pid":"e03e80f190f9f35de564b79afca539fcd3763421","tid":152975,"uid":54697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:11:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但係幾多G佢都列明存喎<br />\n<br />\n你意思係佢QC做假?</blockquote><br />\n有機會係不斷提取同壓縮既過程裏面令到中藥既營養流走左<br />\n我唔識形容，總之沖出黎好淡好淡，同飲開既中藥好唔同</blockquote><br />\n我屋企人做中醫診所都話呢啲中藥粉完全冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c2233908a6227eb46b1ab8af086a598ef6dc8c","tid":152975,"uid":9344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:19:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但係幾多G佢都列明存喎<br />\n<br />\n你意思係佢QC做假?</blockquote><br />\n有機會係不斷提取同壓縮既過程裏面令到中藥既營養流走左<br />\n我唔識形容，總之沖出黎好淡好淡，同飲開既中藥好唔同</blockquote><br />\n我屋企人做中醫診所都話呢啲中藥粉完全冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好講係咪醫師吖，我一個對中醫藥毫無認識既人都覺得佢冇料到，所以我認真地懷疑佢既實際效用<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我本身食緊藥粉，食左一個星期到，每次食完都會身體發盪/feel到個人暈暈地（可能我本身症狀比較嚴重），然後我貪得意去買左一罐農本坊既粉黎飲⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n佢建議份量每次5g, 我同佢飲夠每次15g/一日兩次，都唔夠我飲一次藥粉既效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係覺得好淡好淡，同冇飲過冇分別<br />\n<br />\n枉宜家仲愈黎愈多地方用農本坊d垃圾粉，都唔知收左人地幾錢廣告費<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985d8e48fddd6454c535ed9a4c623659d780efa6","tid":152975,"uid":67996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:08:38.000Z","msg":"咁果d咩同仁堂的藥粉呢?"},{"pid":"308714fc0901162bca6eb5ac14845e9a447d06c0","tid":152975,"uid":9344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:22:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁果d咩同仁堂的藥粉呢?</blockquote><br />\n未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係點樣架？中藥磨粉狀？<br />\n我自己之前都係食緊藥粉，係我睇開果間中醫俾我既，跟住都試過自己出去配<br />\n<br />\n總之農本坊就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"136a78c1cbe5a4f7396ff7fe82d260fde4d9